South America at https://promedmail.org/promed-post?place=8699610,6186. - Mod.TY]

South America
---
Brazil
- Recife, Pernambuco state. 23 Sep 2021. (Reported) 13 278 cases (conf.) death of a 90-year-old woman (https://playcrazygame.com/2021/09/23/recife-confirms-the-first-death-of-the-year-at-a-time-when-it-registers-a-648-increase-in-cases-of-the-disease/).

- Parana state. 14 Oct 2021. (Susp.) 1585 cases, (conf.) 249 cases (https://www.brytfmonline.com/public-relations-confirms-the-first-cases-of-chikungunya-in-the-epidemic-period/).

Asia
---
India
- Ahmedabad, Gujarat state. 9 Nov 2021. (Reported) 399 cases (https://indianexpress.com/article/cities/ahmedabad/cases-of-chikungunya-rise-in-ahmedabad-7615462/)

- Delhi. 18 Sep 2021. (Reported) 60 cases (https://www.hindustantimes.com/delhi-news/malaria-cases-surged-as-dengue-fell-till-september-15-mcd-data-shows/story-sfIMd2oR2LGKG1QlqiL9VP.html).

- Bihar state. 5 Oct 2021. (Reported) 3 cases (https://www.newkerala.com/news/2021/143120.htm).

- Maharashtra state. 15 Oct 2021. (Reported) 1834 cases (https://www.freepressjournal.in/mumbai/mumbai-chikungunya-cases-in-city-surge-by-7875).

